Description: SILK is a 100% J2EE web-based system with a unique set of healthcare.
Headquarters Regions: Greater Atlanta Area, East Coast, Southern US
Full Description: SILK is a 100% J2EE web-based system with a unique set of healthcare development tools, deployed against world-class Oracle database technology. These tools include electronic medical records (EMR) workflows, practice management workflows, HIE, forms development/publishing, report generators, communication tools, claims scrubbing, revenue cycle management, interoperability interface tools, and other rapid application development tools that enable SILK to have a unique software offering in one application and one unified database.  SILK is also not bound to native platforms but has the ability to run on any web enabled mobile device regardless of operating systems or size of the device. iPhone, iIPads, Droids and tablet PCs all run the application from anywhere in the world.  SILK conforms to the specialty, to the office, down to the specific workflow of each contributor of the office in a user friendly format without the need for massive development or customizations of the application. SILK’s open reporting tools allows for data access at the patient, clinical, financial and all other levels of the healthcare lifecycle. SILK is the next level in healthcare technology providing more than just an application. SILK provides the tools to enable your application to grow with your practice as well as the changes in healthcare without the debilitating cost.

Description: Dakotomy is a branding firm born out of the desire to help companies express themselves more authentically.
Headquarters Regions: Greater New York Area, East Coast, Northeastern US
Full Description: Dakotomy was born out of the desire to help companies express themselves more authentically.  In our first year of operation, we recognized many industry myths and challenges associated with branding.  Agencies like to sequester the creative experience; manufacturing a mythical black box out of which, they promise, the most innovative, genius ideas emerge... Look, we think mystery is sexy too, but we’re more interested in taking stakeholders along the journey to optimize together and create a brand that is truly authentic.  Dakotomy’s mission is to operationalize brand through process and education. We work with companies at their foundational level to help mold a more authentic brand leading to faster, stronger, and more consistent communication.  Our job is to create a brand so strong and actionable that your employees can leverage each component for their functional role, and make the right decisions quickly and with more accuracy.  Your brand book will become your bible, and your company will sing the same harmonious tune, all aligned with your business goals and authentic identity.
